rdf:Description.dcterms:title: ISO 639-3
rdf:Description.dcterms:description: Codes for the representation of names of languages — Part 3: Alpha-3 code for comprehensive coverage of languages. ISO 639-3 attempts to provide as complete an enumeration of languages as possible, including living, extinct, ancient, and constructed languages, whether major or minor, written or unwritten.
